org.cef.browser

Interface CefBrowser


  • public interface CefBrowser
    Interface representing a browser.(浏览器接口。文档中的frame(框架)可以理解为HTML页面。摘选自百度百科：HTML框架是借助HTML语言实现的网页技术，可在单个浏览器窗口内同时加载并显示多个独立页面，每个页面称为框架，其布局由特定标签控制，属于计算机编程领域术语。)

      • createScreenshot

        java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<java.awt.image.BufferedImage> createScreenshot(boolean nativeResolution)
        Captures a screenshot-like image of the currently displayed content and returns it.

        If executed on the AWT Event Thread, this returns an immediately resolved CompletableFuture. If executed from another thread, the CompletableFuture returned is resolved as soon as the screenshot has been taken (which must happen on the event thread).

        The generated screenshot can either be returned as-is, containing all natively-rendered pixels, or it can be scaled to match the logical width and height of the window. This distinction is only relevant in case of differing logical and physical resolutions (for example with HiDPI/Retina displays, which have a scaling factor of for example 2 between the logical width of a window (ex. 400px) and the actual number of pixels in each row (ex. 800px with a scaling factor of 2)).

        (获取当前显示内容的(类似屏幕截图)的图像并返回。
        如果在AWT事件线程上执行，则返回立即解析的CompletableFuture。如果从另一个线程执行，则在屏幕截图后立即解析返回的CompletableFuture（这必须发生在事件线程上）。
        生成的屏幕截图可以原样返回，包含所有本机渲染的像素，也可以缩放以匹配窗口的逻辑宽度和高度。这种区别仅在逻辑和物理分辨率不同的情况下才相关（例如，HiDPI/Retina显示器，其在窗口的逻辑宽度（例如400px）和每行中的实际像素数（例如800px，缩放因子为2）之间具有例如2的缩放因子）。)
        Parameters:
        nativeResolution - whether to return an image at full native resolution (true) or a scaled-down version whose width and height are equal to the logical size of the screenshotted browser window(nativeResolution-是返回完全本机分辨率（true）的图像，还是返回宽度和高度等于屏幕截图浏览器窗口逻辑大小的缩小版本)
        Returns:
        the screenshot image(屏幕截图)
        Throws:
        java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException - if not supported(java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException-如果不支持)

      • executeJavaScript

        void executeJavaScript(java.lang.String code,
                       java.lang.String url,
                       int line)
        Execute a string of JavaScript code in this frame. The url parameter is the URL where the script in question can be found, if any. The renderer may request this URL to show the developer the source of the error. The line parameter is the base line number to use for error reporting.(在此框架中执行一个JavaScript代码字符串。url参数是可以在其中找到有问题的脚本的url（如果有的话）。渲染器可能会请求此URL向开发人员显示错误的来源。行参数是用于错误报告的基线编号。)
        Parameters:
        code - The code to be executed.(code-要执行的代码。)
        url - The URL where the script in question can be found.(url-可以在其中找到有问题的脚本的url。)
        line - The base line number to use for error reporting.(line-用于错误报告的基线编号。)

      • find

        void find(java.lang.String searchText,
          boolean forward,
          boolean matchCase,
          boolean findNext)
        Search for some kind of text on the page.(在页面上搜索某种文本。)
        Parameters:
        searchText - to be searched for.(searchText - 要搜索的文本。)
        forward - indicates whether to search forward or backward within the page.(forward - 指示在页面内是向前搜索还是向后搜索。)
        matchCase - indicates whether the search should be case-sensitive.(matchCase - 指示搜索是否应区分大小写。)
        findNext - indicates whether this is the first request or a follow-up.(findNext - 指示这是第一个请求还是后续请求。)

      • getWindowlessFrameRate

        java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<java.lang.Integer> getWindowlessFrameRate()
        Returns the maximum rate in frames per second (fps) that CefRenderHandler::onPaint will be called for a windowless browser. The actual fps may be lower if the browser cannot generate frames at the requested rate. The minimum value is 1, and the maximum value is 60 (default 30).(返回在无窗口浏览器调用 CefRenderHandler::onPaint 的最大速率（以每秒帧（fps）为单位）。如果浏览器无法以请求的速率生成帧，则实际fps可能会更低。最小值为1，最大值为60（默认为30）。)
        Returns:
        the framerate, 0 if an error occurs(帧速率，如果发生错误，则为0)
        Throws:
        java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException - if not supported(java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException-如果不支持)

      • runFileDialog

        void runFileDialog(CefDialogHandler.FileDialogMode mode,
                   java.lang.String title,
                   java.lang.String defaultFilePath,
                   java.util.Vector<java.lang.String> acceptFilters,
                   int selectedAcceptFilter,
                   CefRunFileDialogCallback callback)
        Call to run a file chooser dialog. Only a single file chooser dialog may be pending at any given time.The dialog will be initiated asynchronously on the UI thread.(调用以运行文件选择器对话框。在给定时间，只有一个文件选择器对话框能够处于挂起状态。该对话框将在UI线程上异步启动。)
        Parameters:
        mode - represents the type of dialog to display.(mode-表示要显示的对话框类型。)
        title - to be used for the dialog and may be empty to show the default title ("Open" or "Save" depending on the mode).(title-用于对话框，可以为空以显示默认标题（“打开”或“保存”取决于模式）。)
        defaultFilePath - is the path with optional directory and/or file name component that should be initially selected in the dialog.(defaultFilePath-带有可选目录和文件名的路径，对话框的初始路径。)
        acceptFilters - are used to restrict the selectable file types and may any combination of (a) valid lower-cased MIME types (e.g. "text/*" or "image/*"), (b) individual file extensions (e.g. ".txt" or ".png"), or (c) combined description and file extension delimited using "|" and ";" (e.g. "Image Types|.png;.gif;.jpg").(acceptFilters - 用于限制可选择的文件类型，可以是：
        （a）有效的小写MIME类型（例如"text/*"或"image/*"）
        （b）单个文件扩展名（例如".txt"或".png"）
        （c）使用“|”和“；”分隔的组合描述和文件扩展名的任意组合（例如“Image Types|.png;.gif;.jpg”）)
        selectedAcceptFilter - is the 0-based index of the filter that should be selected by default.(selectedAcceptFilter - 默认情况下筛选器的索引为0。)
        callback - will be executed after the dialog is dismissed or immediately if another dialog is already pending.(callback-将在对话框关闭后执行，或者在另一个对话框已挂起时立即执行。)

      • setWindowlessFrameRate

        void setWindowlessFrameRate(int frameRate)
        Set the maximum rate in frames per second (fps) that CefRenderHandler::onPaint will be called for a windowless browser. The actual fps may be lower if the browser cannot generate frames at the requested rate. The minimum value is 1, and the maximum value is 60 (default 30).(设置在无窗口浏览器调用 CefRenderHandler::onPaint 的最大速率（以每秒帧（fps）为单位）。如果浏览器无法以请求的速率生成帧，则实际帧秒可能会更低。最小值为1，最大值为60（默认为30）。)
        Parameters:
        frameRate - the maximum frame rate(frameSpeed-最大帧率)
        Throws:
        java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException - if not supported(java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException-如果不支持)

      • setWindowVisibility

        void setWindowVisibility(boolean visible)
        Set whether the window containing the browser is visible (minimized/unminimized, app hidden/unhidden, etc). Only used on Mac OS X.(设置包含浏览器的窗口是否可见（最小化/取消最小化、应用程序隐藏/取消隐藏等）。仅在Mac OS X上使用。)
        Parameters:
        visible -(visible - 是否可见)
